  team member can give their best. A leader should inspire, guide and create the
  conditions.
---

A true leader's vision is to create an environment where every team member can give their best. A leader should inspire, guide and create the conditions for their team to be high-performing and fulfilled. They must combine strategic clarity, managerial courage and compassion.
